Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato, I'm out of magaz...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh, be quiet.\NHe's got razor-sharp hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.82,0:00:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of ammo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫The brave choice we wished for♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Its future is being illuminated♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Lycoris Recoil)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.21,0:01:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫If we clash our selfish emotions\Nwe can't see it (yet)♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫To catch up on the distance\Nwe fled from (see) let's go on a journey♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.20,0:01:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Even if we can't see the farthest lands♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫We just burn our lives\Nto keep living in the present♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.62,0:01:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Proof of the existence we wished for♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:02:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫We kept our voices trembling\Nwhile we brandished it♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫No need for regret, we go\Nhand in hand (even the dark past)♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫We accept it and move forward♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Instead of choosing an answer shown to us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫We're aspiring a new dream (always)♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Let's walk along the radiant road♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(#12 Nature versus nurture)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to DA?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alpha-4 has apprehended Majima!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the old radio tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Send in the cleaners.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turning to the cleaners already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are orders from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lycoris are to be disposed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take a look upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.65,0:03:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Not withdrawing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan to do with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily Bell will deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, all Lycoris are\Nto be done away with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? No gunshot wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. They just grazed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've come, Chisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, after seeing that photo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I didn't bring my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you kill Majima for\Nputting me through all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You killed him for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.56,0:04:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't kill him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it falls short of\Nyour expectations, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Do you think\Nyou're Mother Teresa now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I possibly use the life I was\Ngiven again to take the lives of others?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.60,0:04:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only a select few know precisely\Nwhat their roles in life are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you happen to be one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What greater joy could there be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying killing others is my joy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. That's how you can\Ncontribute to humanity and the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:05:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was pretty happy...\Nalthough I wanted to be of help to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you were to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the reason why I decided to\Nwind up a doll on the verge of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doll... A doll, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have a way with words,\NYoshi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That gun doesn't suit you. Give it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you Mika... making this junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What suits you best are live rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outstanding...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move! The next one\Nwill be between your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takina! Put the gun down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshimatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you conspired with Majima\Nto lure Chisato here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you just used Majima, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You also gave those guns to Majima.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:06:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you made Walnut hack Radiata,\Nthen killed him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and you were Matsushita as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, you're the one\Nwho damaged Chisato's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But none of that matters anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as I get my hands\Non that suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi discovered the truth.\NThe key to Chisato's life is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're well-informed, Takina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heart to keep you alive is here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot me and take it for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, you can keep on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come! Don't hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take back your own life and value!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that reason, I'd offer my own life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a lunatic...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding!\NI could never shoot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you won't do it, then I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the point...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never shoot me\Nwith Chisato here, Takina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tear that heart right out\Nof your chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, Chisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use real bullets.\NYour friend's about to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.03,0:08:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. The bullet passed through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate people\Nwho don't value their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you, Yoshi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for your sake.\NWhy can't you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.72,0:09:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's for the sake of the world, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all... the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of things that matter\Nmore to me than the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned that thanks to\Nthe time you gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.99,0:09:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly grateful for what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So live a long life in my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'll be taking back Sensei's bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Takina?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Let me go!\N- Takina! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your heart's gonna get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing Yoshi-san to keep living...\Nthat wouldn't be me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bear to live on\Nin Yoshi-san's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I don't want you to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wouldn't have even\Nlived this long to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because Yoshi-san\Nlet me live that I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just me.\NEveryone's time comes sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But today's not that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you two alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki's really annoying,\Nso hurry up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, it's so windy in here...\Nmy eyes and mouth are so dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Lycoris Recoil)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Lycoris Recoil)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A job?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rescuing the Lycoris?\NWho's the client?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a question for Mika.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Said he had some business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I got this from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, magazines!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I needed these!\NYou see, I lost my bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold on to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What do we do?!\NThey found out about the Lycoris!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DA plans to eliminate\Nthe Lycoris at the Enkuboku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lycoris? But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones for the job are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily Bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're like the boy version of Lycoris.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's hunting down Lycoris,\Nit'll be them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They used to show up\Nat the café all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To try and off Chisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd they stop coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man and Kusunoki\Nnegotiated with the powers that be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Kusunoki's not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I ended up having to\Nhelp out DA in exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuki and the others are in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate all the Lycoris still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can leave their bodies there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Lily Bell units were dispatched.\NHeaded for the Enkuboku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some "clandestine force" you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuki, the Lycoris from Alpha are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like our butts are saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess Takina saved us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are useless as a Lycoris.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disobeying orders and acting on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you show your face here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't they say to stand by?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibana and Erika,\Nyou two lead the Third Lycoris,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get the injured from\Nthe other teams downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not down with disobeying orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to make a name for myself\Nand get promoted to First Lycoris!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura, you come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stay behind and\Nrecapture the control room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're talkin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Radiata's coverage?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.89,0:13:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's currently down\Nthanks to a malfunction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be Robota.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means there's nothing we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go stick that in the Enkuboku's\Ncontrol room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do something about it after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if Radiata isn't operational,\Nthen there's no way to conceal...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, c'mon! That piece of junk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave everything to Walnut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do, Chisato?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! LycoReco's back in business!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where will this flag take us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're off. I didn't tell them\Nyou were the client.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:13:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How soon until Lily Bell arrives?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About 50 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's taking so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The commander likes to take her time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You all right? Hang in there!\N- C'mon, can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Almost there!\N- This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The control room's a straight shot\Nfrom here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think she found her partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the last of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to fill in for Takina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This appears to be\Nfootage from the Enkuboku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man has just been shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more you fight, the more\Nsensational it's gonna be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo PD have still yet to make\Nany sort of announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takina!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:15:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not in charge here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily Bell are on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it quick.\NThey're making their entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them on sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, that pace sure is something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.55,0:16:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, not that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato. The Lycoris are in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here, not here, not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where? Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there really anywhere\Nto stick a USB drive in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,US... USB?\NStop spouting gibberish!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you don't even know\Nwhat we're looking for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A place to stick this in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know at least that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not the time for flirtin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got bad news on the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I can't keep this thing\Nflying forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't yell at me! I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.84,0:17:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right there! Don't push me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move! I can't reach it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good! Not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, c'mon c'mon, almost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it? Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are, Robota!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Please stand by)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you, Robota.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Walnut! I thought you were dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the world's best hacker now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:17:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Located him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh brother, brother, brother... There.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, mister policeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Enkuboku broadcast has stopped,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.55,0:18:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a tip-off has led\Nthe police to the hacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My door!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cracker from the report in custody!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now for Radiata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making me do all the work...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Radiata functionality restored!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it's under someone's control!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Identified as Walnut!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he was still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old-timer... Are you friend or foe?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit your whining!\NYou wanna be a First, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.53,0:18:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're moving in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Lycoris Crisis)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! Were you surprised?\NYou were, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so realistic,\NI was fooled as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Enkuboku will open an attraction\Nwith the secret society Lycoris you just saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No holds barred and packed with adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make your New Year's\Nmemorable at the Enkuboku...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, c'mon! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.03,0:19:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got me good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They spent all that money for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Radiata back online.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beginning internet news\Nand other media coverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato Nishikigi's here.\NShould we carry on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cease your fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get Fuki on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking over command.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alpha-1.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kusunoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like he had\Na grudge against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I have hit him with my smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you done?\NThis thing's gonna crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we'll go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The runt back at the café?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Don't tell Kusunoki\Nor things will get messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.07,0:20:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it'll be like none of this happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My promotion was on the line there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fill in for Takina's position.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I should be the one\Nthanking you instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason she's still here is\Nbecause you got kicked out instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to give your proper thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that what you meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have told the commander\Nexactly what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. What a nasty woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Maybe... Maybe, but still!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dense, the whole lot of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.59,0:21:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What color do you want\Nfor your café uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You disobeyed orders to stand by,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you might get shipped off\Nto LycoReco as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can just wear mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The elevator's almost here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:21:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, no response from\Nthe cleaners sent to retrieve Majima!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.66,0:22:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going down!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! My bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Chisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, here!\NI got this from Takina!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.57,0:22:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.24,0:22:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.11,0:22:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.26,0:22:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫The manga you brought me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫The flower you gave me\Nthat I don't know the name of♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫You're not here yet today?♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.09,0:22:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫I am aware of an emotion never felt before♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:23:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Tracing along a picture decorating\Nthe window, I travel through space alone♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.43,0:23:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫That should have been enough♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫If I were to grab your hand♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.29,0:23:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫This town that knows not of solitude♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Becomes one that I can\Nnever return to ever again♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫You reached your hand out to me,\Nand a shadow is born from the light♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Sing for me to listen\Nthe continuation of this story♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.10,0:23:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Take me to a star that I've never seen before♫
